Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That runt's not fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't working. Forget \Novertaking him, I can barely keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He always pulls \Naway on the corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! What\N the hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already riding on the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So why can't I catch up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one hell\N of a crash, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At least you're still in\N one piece, Beanpole.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then lemme give you some advice:\N your riding sucks.{ik this isn't grammatically correct btw - it's to be antagonising}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know riders can be clumsy, but if they end\N up wrecking their bike, then they ain't shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing like you\N young rich kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather break my\N neck than my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With driving like that, the only time you'll overtake me is in your wildest dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes everything you've got \Njust to not die in a crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That asshole...
