Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai! Hurry up or we're \Nleaving your butt behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition.{if someone has a good onomatopoeia. lmk}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Vroom! Vroom, vrrroom!\N Vroom, vroom!{again, onomatopoeia, one of my many weaknesses}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you, Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating lunch out in the schoolyard has\N been more fun lately, or so it seems. {let's pretend that's what nanchatte means, kthx}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been dying to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai, what are you doing?\N C'mon, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I eat my lunch here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.\N I'm just trying to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, \NI won't bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been good \Nat this kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think \Nyou're going, bitch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands off the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it got to \Ndo with you, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{Doesn't matter what my deal is. \NAll that matters is I'm short-tempered.}Doesn't matter what. Worry about\N how I'm easy to piss off first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One of those delinquent types?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always had a thing for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Delinquents, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully I'm not \Nasking for too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you know someone \Nwho's good in a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,good at riding bikes,\N is really tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and has a gentle smile \Nwith perfect white teeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but he can't be ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And if this special someone drives a bike with \N400cc or more, you just have to introduce me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ito Ai, I'm in class 1-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid can you be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think there's \Nsomeone like that, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a 750cc, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much bigger \Nthan the Road Pal!{https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%9B%E3%83%B3%E3%83%80%E3%83%BB%E3%83%AD%E3%83%BC%E3%83%89%E3%83%91%E3%83%AB - I doubt anyone knows what a road pal is, maybe replace with a more friendly and familiar analogy, like "Girls' scooter"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to ride\N something like this, even just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, I saw one in a movie\N called High Teen Boogie. {https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%87%8E%E6%9D%91%E7%BE%A9%E7%94%B7 - likely this guy - might avoid for reasons idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The lead character in it\Nwas a bike gang leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so cool I could die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided I'd find my own gang leader,\N and fall in love with him, like in the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My lunch got squashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm tryin' to sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't say another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you mind if my\N friends eat with u{\fscx200}—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ichikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.{avoiding ojou-san as cringe}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drop in like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be important\N for you to be here this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for the\N club's regular circuit, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get every machine \Nchecked over by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, we don't have a whole lotta participants this time round.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know anyone, \Nfeel free to bring 'em along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tsukuba Circuit,\N your favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind you riding \Naround at this time of night,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't go doing \Nanything stupid out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm begging you.}That's all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get myself in no fit state to get married, \NI'm all yours, Ichikawa.{kinda difficult to imply the nuance of "If I maim myself in a motorbike accident, I'm all yours"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come and \Nget a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So whenever I couldn't find you, \Nyou'd be hiding around here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. Like I'd \Nbelieve that, you horndog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I can hardly believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She has some real nice legs...{https://jisho.org/search/%20%E3%81%82%E3%82%93%E3%82%88 ??? - not too sure of the word}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you see her flying around on \Na motorbike, hanging on for dear life... {it'll do, shh}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, Gun, \N your bike fixed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi asked if we wanted to go\N to Tsukuba Circuit on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! Anything but the bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it! He's had this \Ncomin' for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And breakin' his bike's the only \Nway we're gonna feel any better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Damn it!\N- No, get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Help, he's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance!\N Go do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you so much as {\i1}touch{\i0} my CB, \NI'll make sure you regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You got away with \Na mild concussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not counting those scratches on \Nyour knees, elbows, and forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a strange one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you'd get \Nyourself hurt protecting my CB.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know why I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just didn't want them \Nto get their hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That bike was \Nshiny and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My bike would've been a \Nlot worse for wear without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to ride a bike, or something like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's only for a while, \NI can give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You really mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:42.07,Default,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fs25}"Auto racing auxiliary facilities"{オートレース補助施設}{Yeah, too blurry to TS properly}{no longer too blurry to TS, but just happen to be too lazt to typeset}{LMAO - Perevodildo}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we could've rode \Ntogether a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the circuit, huh? It's so \Nmuch bigger than I thought it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Best feeling ever. My spine's already tingling just from being here.{note}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure took your sweet time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good reason for this.{/I had to do this}{actually, he says chotto meaning "I was a little forced to do this"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a long story, \Nso I'm not gonna go into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just how it is, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.\N Now who's the horndog?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice of you to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in need of a good race.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I okay to ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm about to race, \Nbut don't go wandering off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him. He's the one \Nthe Princess brought along.{note}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who that rich kid is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but how about we... \N'show him the ropes?' {idk how to make this sound ominous so shh}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Gun! It's your first time here,\N so go easy on the throttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get a feel for the course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong\N with those guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they were waiting \Nfor him to take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are some of \Nthe best drivers in our club,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but their manners \Nneed a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those jerks up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those jerks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure he was \Ngonna go flying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Blocking a newcomer from the inside line... talk about cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've gotta give him credit,\N it barely even fazed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This might get interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This greenhorn is trying \Nto make a move on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drive hard and \Nopen up the gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lookin' good! Damn good! \NGun blew past two of them on one lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My bike's at its limit, \Nbut I can't pull away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Ichikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even have the basics down, \Nbut he's damn fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't exactly \Nseem like a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he's walking a tightrope \Non a windy day without a harness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna take a chance on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As he is now, he's more \Nlike a highway racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is insane! It took me ages to\Neven get anywhere near that lap time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, this little punk...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm faster... I can take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all! It wasn't \Nsupposed to go like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way am I gonna \Nlose to some greenho—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass. You're going in too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Godammit! I ended up screwing \Nup my own throttle work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, speed racer!{meme ish line}{https://detail.chiebukuro.yahoo.co.jp/qa/question_detail/q12224998472}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're comin' next time, right?\N It'll be Suzuka or Fuji next time! {The FISCO circuit it the old name for the Fuji Speedway btw}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is just me thinkin', but I don't \Nthink you've got those hairpins down yet!{Tsukuba has 3 hairpins - one of which is fast, Fuji has between 1 and 3 depending on the layout - with the first one being like a 180-200mph top speed into a sharp hairpin - hence the sass}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go dyin' on us, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what people\N call bike buddies?{It's the best I can come up w/ atm}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome too, little lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it,\N I threw up a peace sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I'm with Gun,\N I get to see tons of new stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.24,0:22:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a brave new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we have a new\N student starting in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.71,0:22:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hijiri. \NPlease, introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Osaka. \NHijiri Hideyoshi's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all about guts\N and nothin' else!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad habits are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I get into fights all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,While I don't always start 'em,\N I always make sure to finish 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that dipshit \Nfrom the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you calling a\N dipshit, you little runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't gimme that shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't it obvious?! \NI transferred to this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teach, I'm done! No way am I \Nstaying in the same class as this dipshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.08,0:23:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal? I'll see \Nthe principal myself if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.21,0:23:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so full of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.92,0:23:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, get yourself \Nexpelled for all I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?! You tryin' \Nto pick a fight with me, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's pickin' a fight \Nwith who, dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the stupidest \Nguy I've ever met!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a gorilla wouldn't\N pick a fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No shit! How'd one of them turn\N up to school, you caveman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a caveman? \NYou little monkey man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd ya say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure was heating up in there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were gonna\N start swinging for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I can't stand that little runt \Nis because I lost to him on a bike before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's really that fast, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.75,0:23:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're not settling this with our fists,\N we're settling it on our bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.13,0:24:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.84,0:24:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't it obvious?\N I'm racing that little runt again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.14,0:24:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I need help!\N Miyuki has... Miyuki has—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened to Mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Some strange guys showed up and\N forced Miyuki in the car with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru, what's the\N meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.17,0:24:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about that beanpole\N from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.38,0:24:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And we just need you out\N of the picture for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.97,0:24:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skull must be \Nthicker than your helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.10,0:24:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.68,0:24:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you're \Nso bent out of shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.10,0:25:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but it takes real scum to\N try something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.11,0:25:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bottom of the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.65,0:25:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumors were right. You really are just\N some rich kid without a care in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.07,0:25:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you quite \Nrealize the situation you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.04,0:25:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you, m'lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.38,0:25:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.38,0:25:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure they\N said the riverbank?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.72,0:25:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.30,0:25:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro, get movin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.39,0:25:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have to ask me twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.70,0:25:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you looking \Nat me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.45,0:25:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You always have that look. You think you can see right into my head, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.58,0:26:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When I... joined the Ichinose Racing Team,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.50,0:26:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you were still in middle-school,\N but I couldn't help being drawn to you.{lol nonce}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.05,0:26:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands so delicate, \Nyet so steady with the machine,{華奢な手足でマシンをあやつり - with limbs that fragile/slender, controlling the machine}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.30,0:26:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and your form{physical appearance} through the corners...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.80,0:26:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd always been watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.43,0:26:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.76,0:26:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,since you've got money, you think\N you can look down on other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.02,0:26:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.93,0:26:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.19,0:26:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, money, status...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.07,0:26:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't you the one\N who's hung up on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.28,0:26:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.79,0:26:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't planned \Non doing this today,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.46,0:26:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but... but now I wanna\N teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.55,0:26:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Ichinose Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.80,0:27:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone so much as touches you, I'll make them regret being born!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.65,0:27:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...{not spoken in the OVA at this point, but added in}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.19,0:27:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A CB750F!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.15,0:27:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.53,0:28:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that \Npunk would show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.20,0:28:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get our own back\N for the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.12,0:28:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you, punk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.71,0:28:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.34,0:28:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.67,0:28:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do to the girl?! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.10,0:28:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.27,0:28:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass, we didn't do shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.64,0:28:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.65,0:28:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta the way!\N Move it, assholes!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.53,0:28:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... how could \Nyou do that to Mi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.28,0:28:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.41,0:28:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.42,0:28:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back in ten years, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.67,0:28:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... I'd rather die than\N let you get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.93,0:29:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You kids can say just\N about anything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.06,0:29:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... that guy a \Nmonster or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.52,0:29:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a dead man!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.69,0:29:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See you in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.40,0:29:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.25,0:29:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.61,0:29:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.32,0:30:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... I thought he\N was just some rich kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.61,0:30:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How wrong could I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.97,0:30:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.43,0:30:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually kinda relieved\N when I heard your bike...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.10,0:30:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Any longer, and I might've done \Nsomething I could never take back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.19,0:30:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,On your feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.24,0:30:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen up, I'll never show myself in front of her as long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.74,0:30:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not giving up on riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.46,0:30:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If we happen to meet on the circuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.00,0:31:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,how about we settle things for good?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.01,0:31:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but you won't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.23,0:31:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.61,0:31:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not hurt, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.11,0:31:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.78,0:31:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.49,0:31:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst is already\N behind us, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.29,0:31:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.63,0:31:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As a boy, do you\N think I'm ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.88,0:31:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.55,0:31:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're real cute,\N and smart too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.06,0:31:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.06,0:32:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I... like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.57,0:32:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, dipshit?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.82,0:32:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You trying to pick a fight again?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.58,0:32:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning, 4:30. I'll be waiting for you at the same mountain pass as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.63,0:32:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.25,0:32:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,'Bout time I dealt with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.58,0:33:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... At the next hairpin,\N I'm staying on him, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.88,0:33:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot. \NThis is no different from last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.35,0:33:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's got a\N screw loose for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.18,0:33:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He jumped his bike to\N get it back under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.61,0:33:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nipping at my heels.\NWhat's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.65,0:33:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How's he still on my tail\N with a driving style like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.79,0:33:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's chasing us?{/pursuing/following}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.87,0:33:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!\N What's that machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.26,0:33:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenging us both, huh? \NI'm ready when you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.97,0:33:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!{muffled and not spoken in OVA}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.52,0:34:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna occupy the inner line from the get-go? \NLike hell I'm letting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.95,0:34:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They overtook me!\N Who the hell is that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.95,0:34:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... that was smooth. \NI didn't even get to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.04,0:34:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You fired up, Beanpole?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.83,0:34:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna go, then go. \NNow's your chance, dipshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.29,0:34:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me\N if you crash out!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.71,0:34:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You really thought I'd back down?! \NI'm not goin' down without a fight! {shh, it'll do}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.40,0:34:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass, you think you \Ncan corner at that speed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.32,0:34:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You gotta be kiddin' me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.25,0:35:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gonna hurt in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.88,0:35:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't hold back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.51,0:35:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't think anybody was \Nstupid enough to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.51,0:35:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither did I, but it\N kinda killed the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.32,0:35:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.11,0:35:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a chick...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.74,0:35:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.74,0:35:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so you didn't \Nknow it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.24,0:35:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure \Nyou're okay to ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.58,0:35:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't show at school \Nyesterday, so I was worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.54,0:35:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I skipped yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.71,0:35:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one hell of a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.72,0:35:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.59,0:36:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't even know Formula 1 models. \NI'd be ashamed to be that stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.51,0:36:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.39,0:36:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always gotta \Nsay something, dontcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.89,0:36:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much of you to look at, \Nbut you're still an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.52,0:36:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, dipshit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.06,0:36:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Got something to say, ankle-biter?{何言ってやんでこのカメ男 - you heard me right, turtle man - no clue what's kame otoko, this seems to be this manga's original invention, it's not used as a common noun, maybe kame/turtle here means "little/short/something earthbound/not tall"}{yeah... I ain't got shit... so... shh}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.78,0:36:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt, \Nbut I've got places to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.44,0:36:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountains will have eroded by the time you're done arguing.{page 165 - ぐずぐずしてるとネズミが出るでしょう この辺 - she refers to the Aesop's fable of mountain giving birth to a mouse, but in manga this makes perfect sense as she adds "on this mountain" and before, the guys brag about with who got bigger balls for two pages straight, here however they merely throw names at each other and don't make big promises so even the meaning of the fable which is "a lot of big talk/malarkey with little results/ultimately fruitless" is inapplicable here, besides, barely anyone would get the reference; konohen is most likely "here/in this place" but I can't exclude "at this rate"}{Also, I hate this line : )}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.59,0:36:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I listened to Hiro \Nand came all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.76,0:36:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought people with skills \Nlike that would end up at my school.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.77,0:36:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposing...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.18,0:36:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposing I get those two together, \Nthey'd make the ultimate combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.44,0:36:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next summer, things are gonna get \Ninteresting at Suzuka, and that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.18,0:37:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is snowing hard, huh? \NGuess I won't be riding any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.18,0:37:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That bike's the only thing on\N your mind, isn't it, Hideyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.06,0:37:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, I heard there was a really \Nbad crash on that pass you drive on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.94,0:37:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.65,0:37:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of idiots\N on the road, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.24,0:37:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's that dangerous there, \Nthen maybe you should stop going.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.37,0:37:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.74,0:37:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.08,0:37:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I... get kinda scared sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.79,0:37:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when I'm waiting for you to come back from your morning ride... I just think...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.09,0:37:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just think,\N if something ever hap—
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.51,0:38:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.80,0:38:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.14,0:38:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so worked \Nup over nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.15,0:38:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoyo, please understand, \NI'm doing this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.13,0:38:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do {\i1}you{\i0} want?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.38,0:38:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with {\i1}you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.09,0:38:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha starin' for?! {顔つけた - is likt to glare at someone / to give them a dirty look}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.51,0:38:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookin' at you makes \Nme wanna hurl!{目がくさりよる - more osaka-ben by look of it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.51,0:38:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who lit your fuse today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.47,0:38:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you wanna piece of me?! {I'm not sure the ippen but is right, I'd just assume it's 一遍ぶっち殺してのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.86,0:39:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? So that's \Nwhy you're all sulky?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.24,0:39:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You two belong in \Nkindergarten, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.75,0:39:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun! Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.83,0:39:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, there's \Nsomething I wanna talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.85,0:39:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about the 4-hour endurance race\N held at Suzuka over the summer, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.48,0:39:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I know about the\N 8-hour race the day after.{ye, the four hour one was for the 'amateurs' the day before the Suz 8 hour for the pros}{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suzuka_8_Hours}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.07,0:39:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.90,0:39:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of entering it under the Ichinose Racing Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.24,0:39:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.41,0:39:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.20,0:39:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you really mean that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.99,0:39:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I need \Nthree more riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.37,0:39:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You serious about this? {changed as he's using the potential form as he doesn't believe it yet. Just roll w/ it for now}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.66,0:39:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll race as two pairs, \Nand I'll be driver number four.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.25,0:40:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me in! Even if I've gotta\Nwork with that stupid beanpole!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.09,0:40:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.05,0:40:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya heard me! I don't jus' race \Nfor fun like you rich kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.89,0:40:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell I'm working with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.97,0:40:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.98,0:40:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enter the race, \Njust this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.69,0:40:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.57,0:40:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.82,0:40:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I say I wouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.62,0:40:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da~!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.91,0:40:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It only took six hours to get here from Tokyo, but we're finally at Suzuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.04,0:40:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.63,0:40:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuka Circuit is even \Nbigger than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.46,0:41:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want each of you to practice \Nwith your own goal in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.92,0:41:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing, we won't be measuring your times until this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.97,0:41:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for the time being, none of \Nyou will know how long you take.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.85,0:41:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.43,0:41:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.98,0:41:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust you to object.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.85,0:41:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This rule was made \Nspecifically for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.98,0:41:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,By trying too hard to lower your time, \Nyour corner entries will suffer,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.73,0:41:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,your bike will become unstable, your corner exit\N will go to shit, and your times would just get worse. {if someone want me to explain this in mechanical/racing terms, lmk : )}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.40,0:41:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's your first time \Nat this kind of event,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.99,0:41:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know it'll \Ngo to your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.57,0:41:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so, instead, I want you\N to focus on your pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.29,0:41:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.66,0:42:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass. You really thought\N you'd post a time that easily? {no clue what he means by "show/demonstrate/give time"}{they tend to 'post' times on a leaderboard - which may only include top 20 or w/e}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.96,0:42:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuka ain't that easy. {/don't underestimate ...} {TLC, guess}{ye, is just  舐める }
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.38,0:42:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take him! {makasen?}{is 抜かせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.10,0:42:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... he's already gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.27,0:42:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do with them? \NI told them to take it easy on the first lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.85,0:42:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,His time on the West course has improved by two seconds since this morning. {ichikawa just said it's their first lap and we've heard him saying they'll only measure it in the afternoon so idk what's this about}{first lap post morning prac. session?}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.27,0:42:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Gun's been sticking\N like glue to the guy in the white helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.70,0:42:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to learn the lines\N from a more experienced rider. {let's just call this paraphrased} {alright, keep your secrets ;^)}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.64,0:43:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.19,0:43:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll settle this later! {TLC, not sure what he means: left showdown in one's custody - likely "let's postpone"}{I assume it's like 後をつける?}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.65,0:43:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.77,0:43:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, he said he \Nhad somewhere to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.61,0:43:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go change, \Nbe back in a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.75,0:44:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! {page 160}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.93,0:44:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, Mom, it's \Nbeen a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.81,0:44:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoyo is doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.98,0:44:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still getting along fine,\N so don't worry about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.53,0:44:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was at Suzuka, and since\N I was in the neighborhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.95,0:44:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd best come \Nsee you before I went back. {VERY unsure what he means, TLC please Touge darling:smooch:, here's manga text, tho it doesn't seem entirely right: せやからどうないしても会って帰ろうと思ってな・・・･}{I assume the firstseya is just 世話 with a bitchin' accent?}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.58,0:44:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have time to buy you \Nany flowers, so sorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.02,0:45:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I got a flat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.15,0:45:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange, how'd I get \None all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.95,0:45:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the \NHijiri household.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.24,0:45:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.30,0:45:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Dad! Mom!\N- Dad! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.51,0:45:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.72,0:45:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.52,0:45:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.49,0:46:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about \Nme on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.20,0:46:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the type of rider who'd have a\N crash on the Tomei Expressway, after all. {東名高速ごときで事故るようなヤワな乗り方はしてへんさがいに from manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.04,0:46:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been saying it's too cold out to be wearing \Na short-sleeved sailor uniform for a few days now,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.01,0:46:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but now that the Sun's out,\N you get reminded of how hot it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.14,0:46:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, when the boys disappear, \Nwe do something a little unladylike.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.89,0:46:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,While summer was hiding behind the rain clouds, \Nwe could tell it was just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.28,0:46:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.65,0:46:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't bring an umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.20,0:46:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, It wasn't\N raining this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.45,0:46:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, everyone knows to bring\N an umbrella at this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.74,0:46:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain never \Nbothered me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.29,0:46:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're out on your bike in the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.67,0:46:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah, it's no fun at first, but the drive home\N feels much better when you're soaked through.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.38,0:47:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost the big day, Hideyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.09,0:47:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That race has been the only thing \Non my mind for the last six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.43,0:47:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know much about races,\Nbut all that matters to me is that you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.48,0:47:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If your bike is maintained and you stick to the rules, safety won't be an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.44,0:47:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If I perform well there, \Nit'll be my shortcut to going pro. {last year, ichikawa said they'll promote him to B-class, I assume this had already happened and becoming a pro is the next step following it}{it's いい成績 w/ an accent }
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.94,0:47:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.90,0:47:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, \Njust let me do my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.62,0:47:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the rain stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.20,0:47:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's so red!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.04,0:47:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.42,0:47:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer's here already.
